00:51:35,630 --> 00:51:39,200
♫  But I love you  ♫

510
00:51:40,000 --> 00:51:45,060
♫  But what good is it now  ♫

511
00:51:50,390 --> 00:51:53,210
I turned on cold water!

512
00:52:16,640 --> 00:52:18,400
Unbelievable. You're drinking without me?

513
00:52:18,400 --> 00:52:20,860
Even your phone is off.

514
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:28,420
It was a hassle to answer any calls.

515
00:52:28,420 --> 00:52:31,590
How did you know I was here?

516
00:52:31,590 --> 00:52:33,520
You come here whenever you're feeling down.

517
00:52:33,520 --> 00:52:36,220
That's not true.

518
00:52:36,220 --> 00:52:42,710
I'm really, really happy today.

519
00:52:48,950 --> 00:52:51,370
Can I get a glass here?

520
00:52:56,480 --> 00:52:59,780
Where would you find an angelic sister like me?

521
00:52:59,780 --> 00:53:04,680
I just forgot my wings up there. I never asked you to run errands for me...

522
00:53:04,680 --> 00:53:05,920
or take your allowance?

523
00:53:05,920 --> 00:53:07,720
Hurry and go find my wings.

524
00:53:07,720 --> 00:53:10,340
You called me to turn off the lights every night.

525
00:53:10,340 --> 00:53:15,190
You would call me saying there was an emergency and when I got there you would say, "Turn off the lights. I'm going to sleep."

526
00:53:16,170 --> 00:53:17,670
You should have told me if you didn't like it.

527
00:53:17,670 --> 00:53:21,390
I thought you kind of enjoyed it because you came whenever I called.

528
00:53:21,390 --> 00:53:24,660
If I didn't come, you'd come to my room and hit me!

529
00:53:25,740 --> 00:53:29,280
It's because you were beat up by me during puberty that

530
00:53:29,280 --> 00:53:33,420
you grew so, so much.

531
00:53:57,470 --> 00:53:59,750
Should we head out?

532
00:53:59,750 --> 00:54:02,640
What are you saying? We're just getting started.

533
00:54:02,640 --> 00:54:06,720
Madam! One bottle of soju, please!

534
00:54:06,720 --> 00:54:08,320
You're drunk. Let's go.

535
00:54:08,320 --> 00:54:12,520
I don't get drunk if I drink when I'm in a good mood.

536
00:54:23,860 --> 00:54:27,430
Why did you turn off your phone today?

537
00:54:30,240 --> 00:54:33,030
It was a hassle to answer any calls.

538
00:54:35,860 --> 00:54:39,210
Are you sure it's not because you were afraid you would call the CEO?

539
00:54:39,910 --> 00:54:43,030
Why would I call that guy?

540
00:54:44,990 --> 00:54:47,680
His flight is at 10:00 tonight, right?

541
00:54:48,490 --> 00:54:52,850
I don't know. Whether he leaves or doesn't...

542
00:55:07,180 --> 00:55:09,400
You're being really weird today. Did you know that?

543
00:55:09,400 --> 00:55:10,800
What do you mean?

544
00:55:10,800 --> 00:55:13,870
I've never seen you turn off your phone because it was a hassle.

545
00:55:13,870 --> 00:55:18,590
Also, you only drink soju when you're feeling down. And you get drunk fast when you're happy.

546
00:55:18,590 --> 00:55:20,550
Your memory is uselessly good.

547
00:55:20,550 --> 00:55:22,270
My memory isn't good.

548
00:55:22,270 --> 00:55:24,900
I remember because it's you.

549
00:55:26,150 --> 00:55:27,590
Go to the CEO.

550
00:55:27,590 --> 00:55:31,960
Go and stop him.

551
00:55:31,960 --> 00:55:34,670
If you don't, you're going to regret it forever.

552
00:55:38,010 --> 00:55:43,760
What makes you think that I didn't try stopping him?

553
00:55:43,760 --> 00:55:48,230
If you stopped him, he wouldn't have left.

554
00:55:50,230 --> 00:55:52,030
Yeah?

555
00:55:56,990 --> 00:55:58,730
Okay.

556
00:56:04,740 --> 00:56:06,790
It's so pretty.

557
00:56:15,700 --> 00:56:18,200
It's a dahlia flower.

558
00:56:29,100 --> 00:56:31,140
Hang on.

559
00:56:50,770 --> 00:56:53,560
Do you know what dahlia stands for?

560
00:56:55,070 --> 00:56:59,380
"Your love makes me happy."

561
00:57:12,520 --> 00:57:17,350
I think you're going to suffer without that person.

562
00:57:17,350 --> 00:57:21,600
I want you to be happy.

563
00:57:21,600 --> 00:57:25,200
That's the only way I can be happy, too.

564
00:57:44,320 --> 00:57:49,630
 Your love makes me happy. 

565
00:57:53,380 --> 00:57:58,400
 I wanted to have you by my side. 

566
00:57:58,400 --> 00:58:02,540
 I won't make the same mistake ever again. 

567
00:58:02,540 --> 00:58:08,230
 Couldn't we just retie a broken connection? 

568
00:58:10,460 --> 00:58:12,570
 You can stop him. 

569
00:58:12,570 --> 00:58:17,760
 You looked really happy when you were dating the CEO. 

570
00:58:26,280 --> 00:58:30,920
 Go to the CEO. Go and stop him. 

571
00:58:30,920 --> 00:58:33,230
 If you don't, you're going to regret it forever. 

572
00:58:33,230 --> 00:58:38,160
 What makes you think that I didn't stop him? 

573
00:58:38,160 --> 00:58:42,580
 If you had stopped him, he wouldn't have left. 

