 The power is off. After the beep– 

576
00:59:03,000 --> 00:59:10,490
Secretary Nam, CEO leave on an earlier flight?

577
00:59:10,490 --> 00:59:12,160
Huh?

578
00:59:13,520 --> 00:59:17,320
Okay. Thank you.

579
00:59:19,330 --> 00:59:22,350
Mr. Driver, please go to Cheongdam-dong.

