01:00:07,190 --> 01:00:09,140
CEO!

582
01:01:01,850 --> 01:01:03,730
Hyeon Joo.

583
01:01:03,730 --> 01:01:06,190
Why didn't you leave?

584
01:01:17,150 --> 01:01:21,600
I felt like I had to give this to you.

585
01:01:43,170 --> 01:01:46,170
"To my beloved Min Joo."

586
01:01:48,030 --> 01:01:54,190
"And to Hyeon Joo, whom I still love."

