01:02:50,770 --> 01:02:56,930
 ♫ I can’t hide all the memories, that’s all ♫  

590
01:02:56,930 --> 01:03:03,590
 ♫ It’s clear again before we know it, ♫  

591
01:03:03,590 --> 01:03:10,670
 ♫ you’re still inside me ♫  

