01:03:22,930 --> 01:03:29,210
 ♫ A promise not to make you cry ♫  

595
01:03:30,700 --> 01:03:39,720
 ♫ The days that I couldn’t keep are painful ♫  

596
01:03:39,720 --> 01:03:41,250
 ♫ I’ll be with you at any time ♫  

